{"tid":1745932,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"修例風波：涉偷拍飛虎隊行動　歷史博物館男職員被捕","createTime":"2019-11-22T13:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T14:28:45.000Z","uid":314577,"like":24,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"f6208531e3be173cc1e2717873729a1ec5bcc452","tid":1745932,"uid":314577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"理工大學及尖東區上周爆發連場衝突，至本周日(17日)，警方出動飛虎隊參與行動，有隊員在理工大學對面的漆咸道南100號、香港歷史博物館內設立行動崗位時，被人偷偷拍下照片及上載到社交網站，暴露了飛虎隊的行動細節。警方經深入調查後，成功鎖定偷拍照片的疑人。<br />\n今日(22日)下午，警方持法庭發出的搜查令，到藍田興田邨一單位搜查，並以涉嫌阻差辦公拘捕一名43歲涉案男子，並檢獲一部手機、電腦、叉電線，以及疑犯當日所穿的灰色波鞋、綠色短褲，灰色T恤及黑色外套等證物返署調查。據悉，疑犯為香港歷史博物館合約員工，工作了6年，案件交由油尖警區重案組跟進。"},{"pid":"010e5055dcf4a0f5489ab4f4ec9ae47cb7e2cdb7","tid":1745932,"uid":37986,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:08:54.000Z","msg":"好on9"},{"pid":"15c7422641a34db3c9949cc36a56452be7db88a4","tid":1745932,"uid":143415,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:09:24.000Z","msg":"真係手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a364dd404ac094421fc084cbd524a51fddfaa937","tid":1745932,"uid":1485,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:09:25.000Z","msg":"其實乜撚嘢為之偷拍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c27f42341390d4fbfdf72dcf57e7e41934b627b","tid":1745932,"uid":13302,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:09:37.000Z","msg":"可以告咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f281ed3e12ed15a8f95e596a5d950eacb95665fd","tid":1745932,"uid":13250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:09:41.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁多人被自殺又唔查"},{"pid":"a53c0a411d763bc4f12ebe6298ad85eec66726ce","tid":1745932,"uid":3